<p begin="00:04:20.794" end="00:04:24.765" space="preserve" tts:textAlign="left"><span style="block">IS IT HARD NOT TO THINK IN YOUR </span><span style="block">MIND "WHAT WOULD JEFFERSON MAKE </span><span style="block">OF THIS?</span></p>


